(40, 6, 24, 6, 24, 15, 15, NULL, 'Serving God vs. Other Masters', 'Both passages emphasize the necessity of choosing whom to serve. Matthew highlights the impossibility of serving both God and mammon, while Joshua calls for a decisive choice between the Lord and other gods.', 'theme', 0.6499999999999999, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
